messages.name: Boba Fett
messages.content: My dad told me this was the best place to meet women.

messages.name: Bossk
messages.content: I've grown weary of chasing Wookiees.

messages.name: Dengar
messages.content: Word on the street says Han Solo isn't the only stunner in this galaxy.

messages.name: IG-88
messages.content: Bleep. Bleep bloop bleep bleep. Bloop bloop bleep. Bloop.

messages.name: Aurra Sing
messages.content: I think I know all of you a little too well.
